{"tid":2321967,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反送中海報展覽 Yellow Objects 奪台灣金點設計獎「傳達設計類」年度最佳設計","createTime":"2020-12-12T02:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T15:23:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"523b5893ef0b59d4572042dfaff841acf87bfa8b","tid":2321967,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:54:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD-yellow-objects-%E5%A5%AA%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%87%91%E9%BB%9E%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E7%8D%8E-%E5%82%B3%E9%81%94%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E9%A1%9E-%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%25A6%25BD-yellow-objects-%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%258D%258E-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E9%25A1%259E-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmi8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=5eec32b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%25A6%25BD-yellow-objects-%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%258D%258E-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E9%25A1%259E-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%2F&h=46836a95\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD-yellow-objects-%E5%A5%AA%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%87%91%E9%BB%9E%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E7%8D%8E-%E5%82%B3%E9%81%94%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E9%A1%9E-%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88/</a><br />\n<br />\n由「台灣設計研究院」主辦的 2020 金點設計獎，昨日（12 日）公布「年度最佳設計獎」得獎名單，其中「Yellow Objects」獲「傳達設計類」年度最佳設計獎。作為去年「Yellow Objects」展覽場地提供單位的 openground 亦在 facebook 公布消息。Yellow Objects 團隊表示，作為香港的設計師，他們有社會責任把數百萬港人的信念用視覺傳達的方法傳播出去。「我們相信設計的力量，我們相信香港人，我們相信自由與公義。」<br />\n<br />\n「在今天張貼一張白紙都可能違法的香港，這系列的作品顯得別具意義和珍貴，感謝金點設計評委對作品的認同，他們所認同的，不只是這 18 位設計師的設計，而是設計的力量，公民的力量，自由的力量。」"},{"pid":"94d57ebc0c2005760a475d0fcd25d5cac1501e93","tid":2321967,"uid":215621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}